flowRoot.flowPara: To make sure everything will be ready and beauty at the openSUSE Conference 2013, Artwork team is working hard and ready to accept crazy suggestions and opinions.

From banners, posters, badges, promo-materials, tshirts, invitation letter, identity.... every thing is doing in a open and transparent way, using trello as our main tool letting everyone that wishes to help to go there and let some comments, help and crazy ideas.
Do you wanna help? just make sure your browser points to https://trello.com/osc13 and hit the enter key in your virtual or real keyboard
